{"tid":2427680,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"財庫局︰現在才知道共產黨的政治紅線可隨心改變","createTime":"2021-03-01T03:27:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T13:56:51.000Z","uid":21470,"like":96,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"100ddece4689084799f0eb35c3c14808440ade04","tid":2427680,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T03:27:58.000Z","msg":"財庫局︰劉焱事前不知有人認為所戴口罩或有港獨含意 <br />\n<br />\n財經事務及庫務局常任秘書長劉焱被報章批評出席記者會時，戴上的口罩疑似印有「港獨」含意字樣的商標。財經事務及庫務局表示，劉焱事前並未留意口罩牌子，也不知道有人認為有這樣的含意，否則一定不會購買或使用。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381031\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2381031&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3Qy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=c74abc0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381031</a>"},{"pid":"f1054a481e1679acb552a917fc58b0eb12b01663","tid":2427680,"uid":8308,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T03:59:07.000Z","msg":"姐係咩?<br />\n支那港獨既含意已經唔知擴大到去邊"},{"pid":"17075385ef91048603b20acd2d530b1dd73ec332","tid":2427680,"uid":53062,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T04:00:31.000Z","msg":"佢帶咩口罩？"},{"pid":"518c759e6f812e8d72709f559d8cfe3fa74f7404","tid":2427680,"uid":20262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T04:02:55.000Z","msg":"暗黃？"},{"pid":"4f6053e8d05b2d5b61241d0c7eafc535cf494583","tid":2427680,"uid":123988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T04:03:44.000Z","msg":"唔通帶光時口罩？"},{"pid":"4142f3c5e39ec13324bc099c121d297805a74a86","tid":2427680,"uid":7766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17075385ef91048603b20acd2d530b1dd73ec332","tid":2427680,"uid":53062,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T04:00:31.000Z","msg":"佢帶咩口罩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T04:03:52.000Z","msg":"救世"},{"pid":"a736bcb668f4889d06559bafc61198ac5db2f788","tid":2427680,"uid":57073,"like":24,"dislike":0